eople from Prussia proper]]\n[[Category:Pagans of the Prussian Crusade]]\n[[Category:Executed German people]]\n[[Category:Year of birth unknown]]\n[[Category:People executed by Germany by hanging]]\n", "name_user": "John of Reading", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:Typo fixing, replaced: latter \u2192 later", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glappo"}
